<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
  <title>로그인 완료</title>
  <style>
    body {
      margin: 0; padding: 0;
      background: #0a0f1e;
      display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
      min-height: 100vh;
      font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, sans-serif;
      color: white;
    }
    .container { text-align: center; padding: 24px; }
    .spinner {
      width: 40px; height: 40px;
      border: 3px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.15);
      border-top: 3px solid #2563eb;
      border-radius: 50%;
      animation: spin 0.8s linear infinite;
      margin: 0 auto 20px;
    }
    @keyframes spin { to { transform: rotate(360deg); } }
    h2 { font-size: 18px; margin-bottom: 8px; }
    p { font-size: 14px; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.5); }
    .btn {
      display: inline-block; margin-top: 20px;
      padding: 12px 24px; background: #2563eb;
      color: white; border-radius: 12px;
      text-decoration: none; font-weight: 700; font-size: 14px;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="spinner"></div>
    <h2>✅ Google 로그인 성공!</h2>
    <p>앱으로 돌아가는 중...</p>
    <a class="btn" href="<%= @deep_link %>" id="return-btn" style="display:none;">앱으로 돌아가기</a>
  </div>
  <script>
    // 즉시 딥링크로 앱 복귀 시도
    window.location.href = '<%= @deep_link %>';

    // 2초 후에도 남아있으면 수동 버튼 표시
    setTimeout(function() {
      document.getElementById('return-btn').style.display = 'inline-block';
    }, 2000);
  </script>
</body>
</html>
